title: Packers looking at "different angles" to make sure they finish stronger in 2026

sources.name: Pro Football Talk
sources.title: Packers looking at "different angles" to make sure they finish stronger in 2026
sources.description: The Packers' season ended when they blew a 21-3 lead in the second half of a playoff loss to the Bears and that collapse mirrored the way they finished out the regular season.
